result.name: Kakure

reviews.text: Very nice place with a great cosy bar and nice spacious restaurant. The menu is very extensive and everything we ordered was fantastic. The bar has a great whisky selection and had very nice friendly people working.

Kakure in a word is all about "experience". To experience the Teppanyaki grill in action and the sushi bar is just phenomenal. Recommend to anyone around Central needing a bit of frills to a lunch date!

Updated 23 June 2019: One review which gave one star had been retracted. This place is a 5!
Wow so I'm the third person to review this place and I just saw how polarizing the other two were. In my opinion unless you find a bug or hair in your foods, you don't give 1 star just because there are mistakes or you think the place is expensive. This place is a 5!! My experience was for teppanyaki only. Look at my photos and see how yummy the dishes were. And trust me they tasted better than they look. The decor was awesome. I felt like I was in Tokyo. The staffs were super nice and polite. We had teppanyaki set for two which included scallops, lobsters, and steaks. ***This place is NOT expensive*** You get what you pay for!!!
The atmosphere and foods make you feel like you are in Japan. Right portion of foods but a bit expensive factored with the cost of location.

Price: HK$400-800pp (lunch) HK$1200+ pp (dinner)
Quality: 👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳
Recommend: 💖💖💖💖

result.name: Landmark Prince's

reviews.text:
Downtown HongKong. Always busy city work busy people. 
The city that never sleep
Best place in Hong Kong to shop luxury.
luxury shopping mall with lot of world famous brands and a dynamic fountain (especcially during xmas & new year times)

It is very wide place and it is also a business place, restaurants and other expensive selling products, and have nice view or decorations,  I went there together with my friends and get some pictures on Saturday night.. there are also show in there like singing a Christmas songs and many people are watching.. very elegant area..
First class luxury shopping environment in Hong Kong

reviews.text: 好👌
•了

Leuke shoppingmall alleen erg duur. Boven zit een heerlijke supermarkt, echt eindelijk eentje vergelijkbaar met Nederland! En de boekenwinkel op de 4e verdieping is ook erg leuk. Met leuke boeken, zowel voor volwassenen en kinderen.
現在的太子大厦、重新裝修、名店比以前多、並沒有老化 。
